# Telemetry sink (MVP 5). Copy to .env.local (git-ignored) and fill in.
# Without any of these, the app runs with a NoopSink — no traces are collected.
# Precedence: VITE_TRACE_URL (self-hosted) → Supabase → Noop.

# --- Option A: self-hosted ingest (Tailscale Funnel'd pip-ingest service) ---
# Public HTTPS base URL; client POSTs to ${VITE_TRACE_URL}/traces.
VITE_TRACE_URL=https://pip-ingest.YOUR-TAILNET.ts.net

# --- Option B: Supabase (alternative) ---
# The anon key is the *publishable* key; it's designed to live in the client
# bundle. RLS (insert-only for anon) is what protects the traces table.
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-PUBLISHABLE-ANON-KEY
